{"title":"春夜的锤声","authors":["陶冶"],"dates":[{"year":1966,"month":4,"day":9}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"春夜的锤声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桂林汽车修配厂工人　陶冶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牛毛细雨满天飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱师傅走出党委会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚步咚咚响如雷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"串串笑声飞出嘴！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“第三个五年计划第一春，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宏伟的远景叫人醉！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党委书记一席话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"句句焊接在心扉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党委书记一席话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好象给炉膛加了煤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烧红咱师傅一颗心呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骤然干劲增百倍。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东思想脑里装，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怕什么任务翻两倍；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大庆精神光辉在，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怕什么人力不足少设备！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"立下愚公移山志，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锻就铁肩和钢腿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闯过千道山呵万道水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只知高兴不知累……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱师傅越想心越热，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跨进车间开汽锤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铿锵的锤声传四方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恰似春夜响春雷。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}